&lt;UL&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;VFR5000 series manifold, metric
&lt;LI&gt;Plug-in &amp; non plug-in styles
&lt;LI&gt;Wiring types (non plug-in): grommet, grommet&lt;BR&gt;terminal, Conduit terminal, DIN connector
&lt;LI&gt;Wiring types (plug-in): terminal block, multi-connector,&lt;BR&gt;D-sub connector
&lt;LI&gt;Maximum stations: 10 (depending on style) &lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;

